nodes.text: A sea monster that inhabited the oceans of the planet Dac was long dead by the time of the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. The creature's preserved remains were discovered around 3643 BBY, and biological samples were taken from its corpse before it decayed completely.
The sea monster, whose physical appearance was never described, was first mentioned in the Bioanalysis crewskill mission "In Its Bones" in the 2011 video game Star Wars: The Old Republic.
